        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Acts 23:6",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ".",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "I am bound with this chain - See the notes on Acts 26:29. Probably he was attached constantly to a soldier by a chain. ",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": "I am bound with this chain - See the notes on ",
            "children": []
          },
          {
